From 34375d4e51697a1f41af9929044bc47bffe2df12 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.com>
Date: Wed, 15 Apr 2026 15:07:59 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] media: imx355: Remove duplicated registers from the mode
 tables

A large number of registers are identical within all the modes.
Move those to imx355_global_regs.

Reviewed-by: Jacopo Mondi <jacopo.mondi@ideasonboard.com>
Signed-off-by: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.com>
